# NetivLang Reserved Words List

# 1. Structural Tags & Boundaries
<Netiv>
</Netiv>
<meta>
<edges>
<book>
</book>
○|
|●
□|
|■

# 2. Control Flow & Function Keywords
fn
return
if
goto
label
syscall
EMIT_PE

# 3. Low-Level Assembler Conditionals
if_z_goto
if_ne_goto
if_z_return
rax_is_null

# 4. Canonical Keywords & Boolean Primitives
°struct
°enum
°const
°bool
°true
°false

# 5. Core Mathematical & Integer Types
°scalar
°f32
°f64
°usize

# 6. High-Dimensional Array & Layout Types
°array
°tuple
°vector
°embedding

# 7. Low-Level Pointer & Mutability Modifiers
°pointer
°mutable
°void
